Roubini, Baertschi, Gieve Own Words on ECB Rate Policy

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-05T21:16:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/roubini-baertschi-gieve-own-words-on-ecb-rate-policy-video-.html
Economists and strategists assess the
 European Central Bank 's policy options amid a deepening 
sovereign debt crisis and slowing economy.  The speakers include  Nouriel Roubini , chairman of Roubini 
Global Economics LLC, Bob Baur, chief global economist at 
Principal Global Investors,  Andrew Sentance , former Bank of 
England policy maker,  John Gieve , senior adviser at GLG Partners
Inc.,  Peter Schaffrik , head of European interest-rate strategy 
at  RBC Capital Markets , and Philipp Baertschi, chief strategist 
at Bank Sarasin & Cie AG. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:56
 